text: "Loosen Up My Strings" is a 1998 song by country singer Clint Black and is the fifth single from his seventh studio album Nothin' But the Taillights. It went to number 12 on the Billboard Hot Country Songs charts and number 6 on the Canadian RPM Country Tracks charts. ==References== Category:1998 songs Category:Country songs Category:Clint Black songs
title: Loosen Up My Strings
